array, every quarter — for a fraction of what the manual version costs in hours.

It's already running on a Vermont operator's 7 arrays across 9 GMP accounts.

Worth 15 minutes to see it on your own numbers? I'll run one of your real arrays
through it so you're looking at the genuine output, not a demo.

